snippet.title: NOM PLANT android gameplay [2019 FHD]
snippet.description:
Help to recruit 100 000 subscribers: https://bit.ly/2HstSlq
Grow long and eat coins in Nom Plant! Avoid obstacles while growing your plant in any direction to get a high score! How long can you grow?

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.luckykat.plant

Features:
* One touch controls
* Smooth gameplay
* Beautiful HD graphics
